VideoPlaybackQualityCreationTime.summary:
The read-only creationTime property on the
interface reports the number of milliseconds since
the browsing context was created this quality sample was recorded.
VideoPlaybackQualityCreationTime.value:
A object which indicates the number of milliseconds
that elapsed between the time the browsing context was created and the time at which
this sample of the video quality was obtained.For details on how the time is determined, see .
